CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1962, pg. 22 reads: "More Visitors - Still more out-of-town guests at the Junior Mothers' soiree at the Hotel Roosevelt, was this quartet who got together for this photo.  Left to right, Mr. and Mrs. Earl Armstrong of Washington, D.C.; Mrs. John D. Grace and Mr. Grace of Willow Grove, Pa. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Mr. and Mrs. Earl Armstrong and Mr. and Mrs. John D. Grace, standing in Roosevelt Hotel for Junior Mothers party
